00:18:41.750 --> 00:18:43.520 align:middle line:90%
But it was just the times.

00:18:43.520 --> 00:18:46.157 align:middle line:10%
You really have to get
the historical context

00:18:46.157 --> 00:18:47.990 align:middle line:10%
and the way people were
thinking at the time

00:18:47.990 --> 00:18:51.120 align:middle line:10%
to understand the
progression of science.

00:18:51.120 --> 00:18:54.080 align:middle line:84%
And in this case, it was
progression sideways,

